{"id": 1206, "genre": 1000, "title": "所以，你去年的年假为啥没休完？", "description": "为什么休不完的年假会作废，做不完的工作却一直在？！（题图来自：John F.Malta）", "record_count": 2092, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160905172055K2Prn8hTBxHcEQMz.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-07T17:00:58Z", "questions": [{"id": 1091, "title": "所以，你去年的年假为啥没休完？", "content": "所以，你去年的年假为啥没休完？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 113455, "content": "没人能够接手休假期间的工作", "image": "img/option/option/20160905173437qy25McC3w9rfaOlY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 113456, "content": "休假前后都要跟同事交接工作，想想就觉得很麻烦", "image": "img/option/option/20160905173635mrnxkwWVagANfdJD.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 113460, "content": "也不是太忙，但看周围同事都不休，自己也不好意思提", "image": "img/option/option/20160905174705m68xXwbOjHPirQBV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 113473, "content": "怕招惹老板，每次请假都会被其质疑“你最近没事做吗”", "image": "img/option/option/20160905180947dNvGLP4I8weO25Ks.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 113475, "content": "本来年假5天，到快过期的时候发现太忙只能请出2天", "image": "img/option/option/20160905181338Xfykc1xIPzCSpUd6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 113476, "content": "如果休假可能就完不成KPI了", "image": "img/option/option/20160905181657tqFaesSWERxH36cg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 113479, "content": "出门旅游要花很多钱，在家又没什么事，就懒得休了", "image": "img/option/option/20160905182012MkT93IheCJEjl2Pi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 113577, "content": "和朋友啊对象啊的年假休不到一起，去旅游也没人陪伴", "image": "img/option/option/20160906000607DsIraiVtzo7e2npc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}